{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e48e4f8c54","title":"中共中央关于曾山同志问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cdd744136f","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":27,"articleId":"e48e4f8c54"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"53b954d860","name":"公安与法律","type":"主题"},{"id":"94b82e4994","name":"中共中央决定、指示等","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"a59dfa2519","name":"各级党政领导人","type":"主题"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"34eb7ab8cb","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于曾山同志问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e48e4f8c54"},{"id":"b6167b90ea","type":"paragraph","text":"一、对曾山同志的错误，可以批判，但性质应由中央来定。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e48e4f8c54"},{"id":"5a58fcd7b6","type":"paragraph","text":"二、曾山同志的活动，听命于中央，造反组织不能干涉。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e48e4f8c54"},{"id":"3ebe99524f","type":"paragraph","text":"三、外来学生不能干预内务部事务，要立即撤出。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e48e4f8c54"},{"id":"85971d12fc","type":"paragraph","text":"四、开批判会搞“喷气式”、大弯腰是错误的，是违反中央规定的，今后不准再搞体罚和变相体罚。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e48e4f8c54"}],"page":{"id":"69997fc088","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e48e4f8c54","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}